column5: I really dont get this scrapbook thing that the girls like to do. But im not going to knock it, for their sake Even though they goofed around with a whitefish pic I had, thanks Destroyed my keyboard and mouse yesterday, thanks Broke the tips off 2 of my rods, geeze thanks I cant wait to see what happens next I guess this makes up for it, geeze thanks Who can complain, my kids are the best  BTW those are my labour rates
What, a whitefish pic. keyboard and mouse and two rod tips or the kids? Is that per hour or per week LOL:whistling:
My stuff per week, other things by the hour, drives me
Boys are easy to put back on the straight and narrow..... compared to little girls that learn to batt their eyes and smile (from their mothers)!!
I have 2 ponds that need to be cleaned up What was bob barkers famous saying
"your the next contestant on ME"  Bob was/is a dawg that has a soft spot for Canadian elephants...
You said it Wayne, and I have 2 if them
So do I Vince, and one boy... I wouldn't give advise blind!
Good job there Vinny! Kids cost lots, but it is a heck of a good investment.   Look at the sign you get and you needed a new keyboard anyway...
True enough but the labour rate sticks
I think it was sumpin' about have your wife spayed or neutered or was it your pets ???
